      <title>随着日本股市接近历史新高，日元看跌头寸增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/cautious-funds-boost-yen-shorts-as-japan-stocks-near-record-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市上涨至历史新高之际，资产管理公司将日元看跌头寸增加至一年多以来的最高水平，这表明投资者对货币风险仍持谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/cautious-funds-boost-yen-shorts-as-japan-stocks-near-record-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 04:19:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
